{"issuance_frequency":"","notes_translated":{"fr":"Vieillissement et maladies chroniques : Profil des aînés canadiens. Il a été élaboré avant la pandémie actuelle et se concentre sur les tendances en matière de santé et de maladies chroniques qui touchent les personnes âgées au Canada. Le rapport fournit les données et le contexte scientifique dont nous avons besoin pour prendre des décisions fondées sur des preuves afin de lutter contre les maladies chroniques, dont certaines augmentent les risques d'être affecté gravement par la COVID-19, et les autres difficultés que rencontrent les aînés en matière de santé. Nous allons surveiller les impacts liés à la comorbidité dans le contexte de la COVID-19 et des maladies chroniques ainsi que les autres conséquences à long terme.","en":"Aging and Chronic Diseases: A Profile of Canadian Seniors. This report was developed before the current pandemic and focuses on the health and chronic disease patterns of Canadian seniors. It provides the data and scientific context we need to make evidence-based decisions to address chronic diseases, some of which increase the risk of severe COVID-19, and other challenges to the health of seniors. Going forward, we will monitor the impacts related to the comorbidity of COVID-19 and chronic diseases and other long-term consequences."},"issn":"","imso_approval":"true","isbn":"","creator":"","org_section":{"fr":"","en":""},"jurisdiction":"federal","private":false,"maintainer_email":"open-ouvert@tbs-sct.gc.ca","num_tags":0,"edition":"","frequency":"unknown","data_series_issue_identification":{"fr":"","en":""},"contributor":{"fr":"","en":""},"maintainer":null,"ready_to_publish":"true","id":"55193d56-e9bf-47ee-a801-3b65e62b2807","metadata_created":"2021-07-26T13:00:57.110330","subject":["health_and_safety"],"pspc_identification_number":"","metadata_modified":"2021-09-27T20:41:22.225517","author":null,"author_email":null,"geographic_region":[],"portal_release_date":"2021-07-26","digital_object_id